    "Use Case 18 describes the process where the Spirit Director generates TCU Honorarium Payment Request Forms for SuperFrog Students who have completed appearance requests.",
    "The system facilitates the creation of these forms by providing the necessary details for each eligible appearance.",
    "This process aims to ensure SuperFrog Student workers are compensated for their services in a timely and efficient manner.Note that the design and the source code of this project are never made accessible via the web, and therefore not part of ChatGPT's training data.",
